WEBVTT

00:04:29.664 --> 00:04:30.712
(Laughter)

00:04:30.736 --> 00:04:32.521
I'm not making this up. I've kept it.

00:04:32.545 --> 00:04:35.182
"Business hours are over at five o'clock."

00:04:35.206 --> 00:04:37.972
She gave this to me
to put on my desk for personal health,

00:04:37.996 --> 00:04:41.265
because at the time, I was working
on my first real business.

00:04:41.289 --> 00:04:44.408
I had no idea what I was doing.
I was working 14-plus hour days,

00:04:44.432 --> 00:04:45.865
seven days a week.

00:04:46.298 --> 00:04:48.592
I was using stimulants to get going.

00:04:48.616 --> 00:04:51.197
I was using depressants
to wind down and go to sleep.

00:04:51.221 --> 00:04:52.412
It was a disaster.

00:04:52.436 --> 00:04:53.940
I felt completely trapped.

00:04:54.645 --> 00:04:58.712
I bought a book on simplicity
to try to find answers.

00:04:58.736 --> 00:05:02.565
And I did find a quote
that made a big difference in my life,